<h2>So we decided, why not design portable audio products that invite you to do the same?</h2>

Instead of having massive marketing budgets that require us to pass high costs on to our customers, we invest in what matters: Minimal design and stellar sound ‚Äî at a price that is as approachable as our products themselves.

We take great care to create things that are reduced to their very essence so we can deliver a sound experience that moves you. Nothing precious. Nothing frivolous. Just great looking audio ‚Äî with sound to match.

How we do it.
<h2>Focused features &amp; functionality</h2>
allow us to do the most important things at a higher level of quality.
<h2>Simple aesthetics</h2>
without unnecessary bling keeps cost and complexity down.
<h2>Acoustics first, marketing second</h2>
just makes sense to us so we can always make our customers‚Äô experience with our products our top priority.

Tom Dudderidge
CEO

‚ÄúWe began with a blank canvas in order to bring a genuinely fresh design sensibility and norm-challenging approach to the traditional CE industry. Our mantra is ‚Äòpassionate about design, serious about sound.‚Äô Delivering on that is our key motivation. We hope that will be self evident when you see ‚Äî and hear ‚Äî the products for yourself.‚Äù

Peter Riering-Cztekalla
Chief Design Officer
‚ÄúWe‚Äôve considered and challenged every detail. It‚Äôs as much about what we decided not to do, as it is about what we chose to embody in our products. In order to deliver premium products at affordable prices, our approach is all about focusing on what matters most: streamlined features and functionality, aesthetic simplicity and prioritizing acoustics over marketing.‚Äù";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"About Us";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:8:"about-us";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-10-04 08:45:02";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-10-04 08:45:02";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:31:"http://nudeaudio.com/?page_id=8";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:1:"6";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-07-10 10:23:34";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-10 10:23:34";s:12:"post_content";s:0:"";s:10:"post_title";s:4:"Home";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:4:"home";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-10-03 08:26:26";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-10-03 08:26:26";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:31:"http://nudeaudio.com/?page_id=6";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:1:"2";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-07-10 10:16:06";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-07-10 10:16:06";s:12:"post_content";s:308:"<div id="contact">
